{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Chris Anderson: Let's now see the extraordinary speech"},{"time":3000,"text":"that we captured a couple weeks ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"Jose Antonio Abreu: My dear friends, ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":19000,"text":"I am overjoyed today"},{"time":23000,"text":"at being awarded the TED Prize"},{"time":29000,"text":"on behalf of all"},{"time":31000,"text":"the distinguished music teachers,"},{"time":33000,"text":"artists and educators from Venezuela"},{"time":41000,"text":"who have selflessly and loyally accompanied me for 35 years"},{"time":45000,"text":"in founding, growing and developing in Venezuela"},{"time":51000,"text":"the National System of Youth and Children's Orchestras and Choirs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"Since I was a boy,"},{"time":57000,"text":"in my early childhood,"},{"time":60000,"text":"I always wanted to be a musician,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and, thank God, I made it."},{"time":67000,"text":"From my teachers, my family and my community,"},{"time":71000,"text":"I had all the necessary support to become a musician."},{"time":75000,"text":"All my life I've dreamed"},{"time":77000,"text":"that all Venezuelan children"},{"time":82000,"text":"have the same opportunity that I had."},{"time":85000,"text":"From that desire and from my heart"},{"time":91000,"text":"stemmed the idea to make music"},{"time":93000,"text":"a deep and global reality for my country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"From the very first rehearsal, I saw the bright future ahead."},{"time":105000,"text":"Because the rehearsal meant a great challenge to me."},{"time":111000,"text":"I had received a donation of 50 music stands"},{"time":116000,"text":"to be used by 100 boys in that rehearsal."},{"time":121000,"text":"When I arrived at the rehearsal, only 11 kids had shown up,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and I said to myself,"},{"time":128000,"text":"\"Do I close the program or multiply these kids?\""},{"time":134000,"text":"I decided to face the challenge, and on that same night,"},{"time":139000,"text":"I promised those 11 children I'd turn our orchestra"},{"time":143000,"text":"into one of the leading orchestras in the world."},{"time":145000,"text":"Two months ago, I remembered that promise I made,"},{"time":152000,"text":"when a distinguished English critic"},{"time":154000,"text":"published an article in the London Times,"},{"time":159000,"text":"asking who could be the winner of the Orchestra World Cup."},{"time":164000,"text":"He mentioned four great world orchestras,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and the fifth one was Venezuela's Youth Symphony Orchestra."},{"time":173000,"text":"Today we can say"},{"time":175000,"text":"that art in Latin America"},{"time":179000,"text":"is no longer a monopoly of elites"},{"time":185000,"text":"and that it has become a social right,"},{"time":187000,"text":"a right for all the people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"Child: There is no difference here between classes,"},{"time":195000,"text":"nor white or black, nor if you have money or not."},{"time":197000,"text":"Simply, if you are talented,"},{"time":201000,"text":"if you have the vocation and the will to be here,"},{"time":205000,"text":"you get in. You share with us and make music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"JA: During the recent tour"},{"time":210000,"text":"by the Simon Bolivar Youth Orchestra of Venezuela"},{"time":215000,"text":"of U.S. and Europe,"},{"time":217000,"text":"we saw how our music moved young audiences"},{"time":222000,"text":"to the bottom of their souls,"},{"time":227000,"text":"how children and adolescents rushed up to the stage"},{"time":232000,"text":"to receive the jackets from our musicians,"},{"time":235000,"text":"how the standing ovations, sometimes 30 minutes long,"},{"time":243000,"text":"seemed to last forever,"},{"time":245000,"text":"and how the public, after the concert was over,"},{"time":248000,"text":"went out into the street to greet our young people in triumph."},{"time":253000,"text":"This meant not only an artistic triumph,"},{"time":259000,"text":"but also a profound emotional sympathy"},{"time":263000,"text":"between the public of the most advanced nations of the world"},{"time":269000,"text":"and the musical youth of Latin America,"},{"time":271000,"text":"as seen in Venezuela,"},{"time":273000,"text":"giving these audiences a message of music, vitality, energy,"},{"time":282000,"text":"enthusiasm and strength."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"In its essence, the orchestra and the choir"},{"time":289000,"text":"are much more than artistic structures."},{"time":293000,"text":"They are examples and schools of social life,"},{"time":297000,"text":"because to sing and to play together"},{"time":299000,"text":"means to intimately coexist"},{"time":304000,"text":"toward perfection and excellence,"},{"time":309000,"text":"following a strict discipline of organization and coordination"},{"time":315000,"text":"in order to seek the harmonic interdependence"},{"time":317000,"text":"of voices and instruments."},{"time":319000,"text":"That's how they build a spirit of solidarity"},{"time":322000,"text":"and fraternity among them,"},{"time":324000,"text":"develop their self-esteem"},{"time":327000,"text":"and foster the ethical and aesthetical values"},{"time":332000,"text":"related to the music in all its senses."},{"time":336000,"text":"This is why music is immensely important"},{"time":340000,"text":"in the awakening of sensibility, in the forging of values"},{"time":346000,"text":"and in the training of youngsters"},{"time":348000,"text":"to teach other kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"Child: After all this time here,"},{"time":352000,"text":"music is life."},{"time":354000,"text":"Nothing else."},{"time":356000,"text":"Music is life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"JA: Each teenager and child in El Sistema has his own story,"},{"time":365000,"text":"and they are all important and of great significance to me."},{"time":372000,"text":"Let me mention the case of Edicson Ruiz."},{"time":378000,"text":"He is a boy from a parish in Caracas"},{"time":383000,"text":"who passionately attended to his double bass lessons"},{"time":388000,"text":"at the San Agustin's Junior Orchestra."},{"time":392000,"text":"With his effort,"},{"time":394000,"text":"and the support of his mother, his family and his community,"},{"time":399000,"text":"he became a principal member"},{"time":401000,"text":"in the double bass segment of the Berlin Philharmonic Orchestra."},{"time":405000,"text":"We have another well-known case -- Gustavo Dudamel."},{"time":410000,"text":"He started as a boy member of the children's orchestra"},{"time":414000,"text":"in his hometown, Barquisimeto."},{"time":416000,"text":"There, he grew as a violinist and as a conductor."},{"time":422000,"text":"He became the conductor of Venezuela's junior orchestras,"},{"time":427000,"text":"and today conducts the world's greatest orchestras."},{"time":431000,"text":"He is the musical director of Los Angeles Philharmonic,"},{"time":436000,"text":"and is still the overall leader of Venezuela's junior orchestras."},{"time":440000,"text":"He was the conductor of the Gothenburg Symphony Orchestra,"},{"time":442000,"text":"and he's an unbeatable example"},{"time":446000,"text":"for young musicians in Latin America and the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450000,"text":"The structure of El Sistema"},{"time":452000,"text":"is based on a new and flexible managing style"},{"time":459000,"text":"adapted to the features of each community and region,"},{"time":465000,"text":"and today attends to 300,000 children of the lower and middle class"},{"time":471000,"text":"all over Venezuela."},{"time":473000,"text":"It's a program of social rescue"},{"time":477000,"text":"and deep cultural transformation"},{"time":481000,"text":"designed for the whole Venezuelan society"},{"time":485000,"text":"with absolutely no distinctions whatsoever,"},{"time":487000,"text":"but emphasizing the vulnerable and endangered social groups."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494000,"text":"The effect of El Sistema is felt in three fundamental circles:"},{"time":499000,"text":"in the personal/social circle,"},{"time":502000,"text":"in the family circle and in the community."},{"time":507000,"text":"In the personal/social circle,"},{"time":509000,"text":"the children in the orchestras and choirs"},{"time":514000,"text":"develop their intellectual and emotional side."},{"time":518000,"text":"The music becomes a source"},{"time":520000,"text":"for developing the dimensions of the human being,"},{"time":524000,"text":"thus elevating the spirit"},{"time":526000,"text":"and leading man to a full development of his personality."},{"time":530000,"text":"So, the emotional and intellectual profits are huge --"},{"time":537000,"text":"the acquisition of leadership, teaching and training principles,"},{"time":546000,"text":"the sense of commitment, responsibility,"},{"time":548000,"text":"generosity and dedication to others,"},{"time":552000,"text":"and the individual contribution to achieve great collective goals."},{"time":559000,"text":"All this leads to the development of self-esteem and confidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"Mother Teresa of Calcutta"},{"time":571000,"text":"insisted on something that always impressed me:"},{"time":575000,"text":"the most miserable and tragic thing about poverty"},{"time":580000,"text":"is not the lack of bread or roof,"},{"time":585000,"text":"but the feeling of being no-one --"},{"time":589000,"text":"the feeling of not being anyone,"},{"time":591000,"text":"the lack of identification,"},{"time":596000,"text":"the lack of public esteem."},{"time":602000,"text":"That's why the child's development"},{"time":605000,"text":"in the orchestra and the choir"},{"time":608000,"text":"provides him with a noble identity"},{"time":610000,"text":"and makes him a role model for his family and community."},{"time":616000,"text":"It makes him a better student at school"},{"time":621000,"text":"because it inspires in him a sense of responsibility,"},{"time":623000,"text":"perseverance and punctuality that will greatly help him at school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632000,"text":"Within the family, the parents' support is unconditional."},{"time":639000,"text":"The child becomes a role model for both his parents,"},{"time":643000,"text":"and this is very important for a poor child."},{"time":645000,"text":"Once the child discovers he is important to his family,"},{"time":651000,"text":"he begins to seek new ways of improving himself"},{"time":655000,"text":"and hopes better for himself and his community."},{"time":660000,"text":"Also, he hopes for social and economic improvements for his own family."},{"time":667000,"text":"All this makes up a constructive and ascending social dynamic."},{"time":674000,"text":"The large majority of our children belong, as I already mentioned,"},{"time":679000,"text":"to the most vulnerable strata of the Venezuelan population."},{"time":683000,"text":"That encourages them to embrace new dreams, new goals,"},{"time":688000,"text":"and progress in the various opportunities"},{"time":692000,"text":"that music has to offer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694000,"text":"Finally, in the circle of the community,"},{"time":698000,"text":"the orchestras prove to be the creative spaces of culture"},{"time":703000,"text":"and sources of exchange and new meanings."},{"time":705000,"text":"The spontaneity music has"},{"time":711000,"text":"excludes it as a luxury item and makes it a patrimony of society."},{"time":718000,"text":"It's what makes a child play a violin at home,"},{"time":723000,"text":"while his father works in his carpentry."},{"time":727000,"text":"It's what makes a little girl play the clarinet at home,"},{"time":732000,"text":"while her mother does the housework."},{"time":736000,"text":"The idea is that the families join with pride and joy"},{"time":743000,"text":"in the activities of the orchestras and the choirs"},{"time":745000,"text":"that their children belong to."},{"time":747000,"text":"The huge spiritual world that music produces in itself,"},{"time":752000,"text":"which also lies within itself,"},{"time":755000,"text":"ends up overcoming material poverty."},{"time":759000,"text":"From the minute a child's taught how to play an instrument,"},{"time":761000,"text":"he's no longer poor."},{"time":763000,"text":"He becomes a child in progress heading for a professional level,"},{"time":768000,"text":"who'll later become a full citizen."},{"time":770000,"text":"Needless to say that music is the number one prevention"},{"time":776000,"text":"against prostitution, violence, bad habits,"},{"time":780000,"text":"and everything degrading in the life of a child."}]},{"cues":[{"time":785000,"text":"A few years ago, historian Arnold Toynbee"},{"time":791000,"text":"said that the world was suffering a huge spiritual crisis."},{"time":797000,"text":"Not an economic or social crisis, but a spiritual one."},{"time":802000,"text":"I believe that to confront such a crisis,"},{"time":808000,"text":"only art and religion can give proper answers to humanity,"},{"time":817000,"text":"to mankind's deepest aspirations,"},{"time":819000,"text":"and to the historic demands of our times."},{"time":823000,"text":"Education -- the synthesis of wisdom and knowledge --"},{"time":831000,"text":"is the means to strive for a more perfect, more aware,"},{"time":840000,"text":"more noble and more just society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"With passion and enthusiasm we pay profound respects to TED"},{"time":856000,"text":"for its outstanding humanism, the scope of its principles,"},{"time":865000,"text":"for its open and generous promotion of young values."},{"time":873000,"text":"We hope that TED can contribute in a full and fundamental way"},{"time":881000,"text":"to the building of this new era in the teaching of music,"},{"time":885000,"text":"in which the social, communal, spiritual and vindicatory aims"},{"time":893000,"text":"of the child and the adolescent"},{"time":895000,"text":"become a beacon and a goal for a vast social mission."},{"time":900000,"text":"No longer putting society at the service of art,"},{"time":906000,"text":"and much less at the services of monopolies of the elite,"},{"time":910000,"text":"but instead art at the service of society,"},{"time":914000,"text":"at the service of the weakest, at the service of the children,"},{"time":918000,"text":"at the service of the sick, at the service of the vulnerable,"},{"time":923000,"text":"and at the service of all those who cry for vindication"},{"time":928000,"text":"through the spirit of their human condition"},{"time":932000,"text":"and the raising up of their dignity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":934000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":938000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":939000,"text":"CA: We are going live now to Caracas."},{"time":942000,"text":"We are going live to Caracas"},{"time":944000,"text":"to hear Maestro Abreu's TED Prize wish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":948000,"text":"JA: Here is my TED Prize wish:"},{"time":952000,"text":"I wish that you'll help to create and document"},{"time":957000,"text":"a special training program"},{"time":961000,"text":"for 50 gifted young musicians,"},{"time":964000,"text":"passionate about their art and social justice,"},{"time":969000,"text":"and dedicated to bringing El Sistema to the United States"},{"time":975000,"text":"and other countries."},{"time":977000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":979000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}